description: Turnkey Two-Family in Prime South Boston | 6% Cap RateFully renovated and income-producing two-family located on a quiet, private street in South Boston with only a handful of homes. The property features a 5-bedroom, 2-bath duplex on the upper floors and a 1-bedroom, 1-bath unit on the first floor. Both units offer new kitchens, updated bathrooms, private rear decks, and efficient heating and A/C. Building-wide electrical systems have been updated, and the property has been well-maintained throughout. Currently generating $9,550/month, with rents increasing to $9,750/month in September, this property delivers a 6% cap rate in a highly desirable rental market.
